channel.description:
Search //rune until you find remove id repeating under the last } add:
[code]//Rares if(removeID == 1053 || removeID == 1050 || removeID == 3481 || removeID == 1055 || removeID == 1052 || removeID == 3483 || removeID == 1057 || removeID == 4214 || removeID == 3485 || removeID == 1038 || removeID == 4224 || removeID == 3486 || removeID == 1042 || removeID == 4151 || removeID == 3488 || removeID == 1044 || removeID == 1229 || removeID == 1377 || removeID == 1046 || removeID == 1231 || removeID == 6569) { return 2365; }[/code]
To smith you need perfect gold bar. I made this myself. [glow=red,2,300]Post what you think of this![/glow]
